headline: D-Wave Quantum (QBTS) Loses 11.8% as 2 Tech Giants Could Threaten its Competitive Edge
summary: D-Wave Quantum Inc. (NYSE:QBTS) is one of the stocks drowned heavily. Are you holding any? D-Wave dropped its share prices by 11.8 percent week-on-week as investors unloaded positions over fears that the aggressive expansion moves of two technology giants into the quantum computing industry could threaten its competitive edge.
